data.description: Amazing home with perfect location! Close distance to George Eisenhut Elementary and Eisenhut Park. Easy access to the 99 along with the Vintage Fair mall. This home boasts recently renovated kitchen and bathrooms inside with newer paint throughout. Out back is a beautiful pool with a built in deck to beat the valley heat. Need extra space for recreational vehicles? This home will have you covered with RV parking. Do not miss this opportunity. Listing agent is related to seller.
